    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1873-02-15T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1873-02-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="84"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d84">
                <head>No. 390.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">General <persName corresp="#p_DES1" type="from"
                            >Sickles</persName> to Mr. <persName corresp="#p_HF1" type="to"
                            >Fish</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1873-02-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">February</hi> 15, 1873</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Officially received to-day, with great ceremony, by Chief Executive
                        <persName>Figueras</persName>, and also by president of sovereign assembly,
                        <persName>Martos</persName>. Addresses of each most friendly. Shall I report
                    remarks by cable? Proceedings reported to assembly by
                        <persName>Castelar</persName> in brief and brilliant speech. Order assured;
                    funds rising$ confidence established.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_DES1">SICKLES</persName>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
